modules.prop65WarningDetail: WARNING: This product can expose you to chemicals which are known to the state of California to cause cancer
modules.description:
#### Benefits

- Full-coverage formula with natural matte finish
- Smooths & brightens appearance for an instant eye lift effect
- Crease-proof formula won’t cake or settle with 16 hrs of flawless wear
- Tape Technology™ helps smooth & blur appearance of fine lines & wrinkles
- Applies easily with jumbo Speed Smoother™
- Not ready to commit? Shop travel-size!

#### Features

- 100% agree it doesn’t crease or look cakey
- 100% agree skin looks & feels smoother
- 100% agree undereyes look smoother
- 100% agree it covers dark circles
- 100% would recommend to a friend
- 97% agree it blurs & smooths appearance of wrinkles & fine lines
- 16-hr longwear
- 12-hr crease proof
- Waterproof
- Dermatologist tested
- *based on a clinical & consumer panel study of 32 subjects

#### Key Ingredients

- Shea butter: moisturizes & conditions
- Mango butter: helps moisturize & condition skin
- Licorice root: brightens & color corrects look of skin
modules.usage:
for a face lift effect:  
- conceal dark circles  
- dot \& dash concealer onto undereyes  
- blend upward towards temples with a makeup sponge or concealer brush  
- full face of flawless  
- dot or dash directly onto redness, blemishes or imperfections  
- blend from center of face outwards with a makeup sponge or concealer brush   
- PRO tips:  
- if using a sponge, dampen for smoother application  
- use on eyelids as a shadow primer for a lasting look

modules.description: Swipe on the hype with Shape Tape, tarte's best-selling full-coverage concealer!
modules.positiveHeadline: Hands Down - BEST CONCEALER I HAVE EVER USED
modules.positiveComments:
I am almost 30, and have started to get some wrinkling and fine lines around my eyes. I have been on a hunt for the best concealer for under my eyes, something to cover and brighten my dark circles but also won't settle in my fine lines. THIS PRODUCT IS WHAT I HAVE BEEN SEARCHING FOR!

I watch a lot of young You Tubers that recommend different concealers and always say how they products they use "don't crease under their eyes" - well yeah, because you're 20 years old and you have no wrinkles!!

I have tried the following concealer brands and ALL crease for me: NYX, Too Faced, IT Cosmetics, Hard Candy, Maybelline, Loreal, and lastly the Urban Decay Naked concealer and every single one settles into fine lines around my eyes and creases. So when I was told by my friend that works at ULTA that the Shape Tape was her new Holy Grail and she would never use anything else again (and she is 35 so she has similar aged skin to mine) I had to try it out and oh my god, this stuff is MAGIC!

It doesn't crease, doesn't sit in fine lines, is super full coverage and covers my dark circles but isn't drying like most full coverage concealer, it literally blurs the fine lines and its almost like they are no longer there and gives the most beautiful finish. 

My new Ride or Die concealer..... Im in LOVE

Only complaint: Shade range - there needs to be more shades because there are some pretty big jumps between some of the shades, but everything else is amazing. 

If you're over 30 and need a full coverage concealer that won't make your wrinkles stand out, you NEED this!

One more thing: It is exclusive to ULTA - so you better get it quick because my Ulta is already almost sold out and it looks like they are sold out of some shades online already.
modules.negativeComments: I bought this twice and returned it twice. I tried to love it, I really did! It was too dry for my under eyes and did not stay on when I used it to conceal imperfections. I don't have weird skin, I'm not super oily or really dry. I lean towards combination to dry. Of course, just like everyone else, I bent because every beauty guru on YouTube raves about it. The first time I got it I thought maybe I didn't like it because the shade was off. The second time I got it, the shade was fine but it emphasized the little lines under my eyes so bad! I take great care of my skin, there's no reason it should age me! I'm only 32, I don't need a concealer to make me look older! Sorry, I know everyone loves this, but I wanted to be honest about my experience. Sometimes, things just don't work for your skin. This didn't work for mine.

reviews.headline: Don't believe the hype. Try it in store first
reviews.comment: I wish I had tried this in store. I got it half off but still consider it a waste as I just want to get through the tube. It's sticky and dries too quick even with eye cream applied first. It doesn't blend well or provide good coverage. I think it just got hype on stupid TT social media but it doesn't deserve the hype at all.

reviews.headline: don't like it
reviews.comment: hard to blend and creases. you could tell that i was wearing concelear whihc i dont really like. i recommend other concelears over this one. i really like the nars one

reviews.headline: Love this!!
reviews.comment: Been using this for 2 years and I love it. It's light and has good coverage.

reviews.headline: I like it but I'm confused
reviews.comment: Ive been using this a ling time. I have some acne scars on my cheeks and it covers really well under my tarte foundation. This last bottle I got looked brand new, but was almost empty…? I dont have the package from the old one so im not sure how many fl oz it was. The old one did squish out a lot so i guess it makes sense to put less in but it costs more now than before.
